				Author: Althaf Ahamed Sadique

   Purpose : The purpose of this program is to ask for some events that want to be recorded.These
   	   events are either School or Work events. The school events are in ascending order of date whereas the
	   work events are in ascending order of priority.
	     These events are then printed out.

	      	      	      List of source/header/data files:

			      source		header
			      
			      Calender.cc	Calender.h
			      Event.cc		Event.h
			      Date.cc		Date.h
			      Time.cc		Time.h
			      WorkEvent.cc	WorkEvent.h
			      SchoolEvent.cc	SchoolEvent.h
			      main.cc
			      WorkEvent.cc

	      Compilation: To compile Assignment 3, use "make" command to compile everything. To compile
	      		   a specific class use "make ClassName.o".

             Launching: Execute the program using the command "./a3 < in.txt" where in.txt contains inputs. To check for memory leaks
	     		use "valgrind ./a3 < in.txt"
		

	
